## Key Observations

- Digit **1** achieved the highest F1-score (0.99) — distinct vertical stroke makes it easy to classify
- Digit **2** had the lowest precision (0.92) — occasionally confused with 3 and 7
- Loss converged quickly within just 2 epochs, demonstrating the efficiency of Adam optimiser on MNIST
- The model generalises well with no signs of overfitting
